eathers.'\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 4085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4010, \"end\": 4018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8843222567064247e-18, \"text\": \"Fox News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an article\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4006}, {\"ngram\": \"Drag performer\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4045}, {\"ngram\": \"feathers\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am like, yeah,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"First and foremost, it was definitely an honor.\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4166, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an honor\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France took very seriously the role of being the host of these Olympics, and we really wanted to showcase the depth of French culture.\", \"from\": 4167, \"to\": 4301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4167, \"end\": 4173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999818859408948, \"rank\": 1.811305051104162e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 4286, \"end\": 4300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the role\", \"from\": 4194, \"to\": 4202}, {\"ngram\": \"the host\", \"from\": 4212, \"to\": 4220}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4238}, {\"ngram\": \"the depth\", \"from\": 4273, \"to\": 4282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not just about queer people or drag, it was also about waacking, about the ballroom scene, about vogueing, about hip hop.\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 4325, \"to\": 4337}, {\"ngram\": \"waacking\", \"from\": 4365, \"to\": 4373}, {\"ngram\": \"the ballroom scene\", \"from\": 4381, \"to\": 4399}, {\"ngram\": \"vogueing\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4415}, {\"ngram\": \"hip hop\", \"from\": 4423, \"to\": 4430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was all about music and celebration and a big banquet and a big party.\", \"from\": 4432, \"to\": 4505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 4449, \"to\": 4454}, {\"ngram\": \"celebration\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4470}, {\"ngram\": \"a big banquet\", \"from\": 4475, \"to\": 4488}, {\"ngram\": \"a big party\", \"from\": 4493, \"to\": 4504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It made sense to come back as Joan of Arc, because I always said that I would have my revenge.\", \"from\": 4507, \"to\": 4601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 4515, \"to\": 4520}, {\"ngram\": \"Joan\", \"from\": 4537, \"to\": 4541}, {\"ngram\": \"Arc\", \"from\": 4545, \"to\": 4548}, {\"ngram\": \"my revenge\", \"from\": 4590, \"to\": 4600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What I love about Thomas Jolly is that he really allowed us to do our own thing.\", \"from\": 4602, \"to\": 4682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4620, \"end\": 4626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9999895517503455, \"rank\": 9.063999973335023e-06, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4661}, {\"ngram\": \"our own thing\", \"from\": 4668, \"to\": 4681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So my outfit was completely my decision.\", \"from\": 4683, \"to\": 4723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my outfit\", \"from\": 4686, \"to\": 4695}, {\"ngram\": \"my decision\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I definitely wanted to pay homage to where I come from, which was Season 12 of \\\"RuPaul's Drag Race\\\" to now being a host of \\\"Drag Race France\\\" and to be able to come back in France as a warrior for French people and for freedom.\", \"from\": 4724, \"to\": 4951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4897, \"end\": 4903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999818859408948, \"rank\": 1.811305051104162e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 4921, \"end\": 4934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"homage\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4757}, {\"ngram\": \"Season\", \"from\": 4790, \"to\": 4796}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"RuPaul's Drag Race\", \"from\": 4803, \"to\": 4822}, {\"ngram\": \"a host\", \"from\": 4837, \"to\": 4843}, {\"ngram\": \"Drag Race France\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4864}, {\"ngram\": \"a warrior\", \"from\": 4907, \"to\": 4916}, {\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 4943, \"to\": 4950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, with the scandal around it, I think that Joan of Arc was an even better decision for an outfit.\", \"from\": 4952, \"to\": 5052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scandal\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4973}, {\"ngram\": \"Joan\", \"from\": 4998, \"to\": 5002}, {\"ngram\": \"Arc\", \"from\": 5006, \"to\": 5009}, {\"ngram\": \"an even better decision\", \"from\": 5014, \"to\": 5037}, {\"ngram\": \"an outfit\", \"from\": 5042, \"to\": 5051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About 80% of the feedback that I have received has been positive.\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"About 80%\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5063}, {\"ngram\": \"the feedback\", \"from\": 5067, \"to\": 5079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was very moved by realizing how much of a platform the Olympics were.\", \"from\": 5120, \"to\": 5191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a platform\", \"from\": 5162, \"to\": 5172}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5173, \"to\": 5185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was able to not just make my own community in France or in the U.S. proud, (but) I was receiving messages from people in Korea, people in Japan, in Brazil, in Peru, in Muslim countries.\", \"from\": 5192, \"to\": 5379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5240, \"end\": 5246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999818859408948, \"rank\": 1.811305051104162e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5315, \"end\": 5320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9712648177057635, \"rank\": 0.02957597767046675, \"text\": \"Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 5332, \"end\": 5337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.7276087400892255, \"rank\": 0.37237872981189585, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 5342, \"end\": 5348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9999992129517892, \"rank\": 4.6134705242129644e-07, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 5353, \"end\": 5357,