aconservativefeather.\", \"from\": 5679, \"to\": 5738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But also, that feather has been around me since I was born just for being born, so that was never something that I would be scared of.\", \"from\": 5739, \"to\": 5873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"feather\", \"from\": 5754, \"to\": 5761}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5837, \"to\": 5846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did actually interact with some of the DMs that I received from people who were more moderate in their attacks.\", \"from\": 5875, \"to\": 5988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the DMs\", \"from\": 5912, \"to\": 5919}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5941, \"to\": 5947}, {\"ngram\": \"their attacks\", \"from\": 5974, \"to\": 5987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I started talking to this woman who is very conservative and Christian and has a 14-year-old kid, and I started to debunk a little bit of the things that she assumed.\", \"from\": 5989, \"to\": 6155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this woman\", \"from\": 6010, \"to\": 6020}, {\"ngram\": \"a 14-year-old kid\", \"from\": 6068, \"to\": 6085}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 6111, \"to\": 6123}, {\"ngram\": \"the things\", \"from\": 6127, \"to\": 6137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Within a five-minute conversation, that woman said to me, \\\"How can I watch 'Drag Race France' because now I want to see what you do.'\\\"\", \"from\": 6156, \"to\": 6290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6232, \"end\": 6248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Drag Race France\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a five-minute conversation\", \"from\": 6163, \"to\": 6189}, {\"ngram\": \"that woman\", \"from\": 6191, \"to\": 6201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I could spend 10, 15 minutes with every single one of these people putting a vomit emoji or \\\"you are going to burn in hell\\\" comment, I would, but I can not.\", \"from\": 6291, \"to\": 6450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these people\", \"from\": 6348, \"to\": 6360}, {\"ngram\": \"a vomit\", \"from\": 6369, \"to\": 6376}, {\"ngram\": \"hell\", \"from\": 6412, \"to\": 6416}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" comment\", \"from\": 6416, \"to\": 6425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that at the time, queer people existed and were welcomed as long as they were the buffoons that are here to entertain people.\", \"from\": 6452, \"to\": 6585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 6468, \"to\": 6476}, {\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 6478, \"to\": 6490}, {\"ngram\": \"the buffoons\", \"from\": 6538, \"to\": 6550}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6578, \"to\": 6584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But having queer people on the forefront of the festivities and represent the pride of what France is, and having an influential drag queen performing her song, then that becomes too much because we should not have to shove our life in their faces.\", \"from\": 6586, \"to\": 6834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6678, \"end\": 6684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999818859408948, \"rank\": 1.811305051104162e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 6597, \"to\": 6609}, {\"ngram\": \"the forefront\", \"from\": 6613, \"to\": 6626}, {\"ngram\": \"the festivities\", \"from\": 6630, \"to\": 6645}, {\"ngram\": \"the pride\", \"from\": 6660, \"to\": 6669}, {\"ngram\": \"an influential drag queen\", \"from\": 6700, \"to\": 6725}, {\"ngram\": \"her song\", \"from\": 6737, \"to\": 6745}, {\"ngram\": \"our life\", \"from\": 6810, \"to\": 6818}, {\"ngram\": \"their faces\", \"from\": 6822, \"to\": 6833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well,guess what, Mimi?We both have the right to vote.\", \"from\": 6835, \"to\": 6888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mimi?We\", \"from\": 6852, \"to\": 6859}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 6870, \"to\": 6879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Absolutely.\", \"from\": 6890, \"to\": 6901, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Never at any point in the conversation was it mentioned that we would redefine a Biblical moment.\", \"from\": 6902, \"to\": 6999, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any point\", \"from\": 6911, \"to\": 6920}, {\"ngram\": \"the conversation\", \"from\": 6924, \"to\": 6940}, {\"ngram\": \"a Biblical moment\", \"from\": 6981, \"to\": 6998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was always about being Greek gods and a big banquet at this table turning into a runway, and it's a massive celebration and festivity.\", \"from\": 7000, \"to\": 7137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7026, \"end\": 7036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.9982380265692833, \"rank\": 0.0017650834611637107, \"text\": \"Greek gods\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big banquet\", \"from\": 7041, \"to\": 7054}, {\"ngram\": \"this table\", \"from\": 7058, \"to\": 7068}, {\"ngram\": \"a runway\", \"from\": 7082, \"to\": 7090}, {\"ngram\": \"a massive celebration\", \"from\": 7101, \"to\": 7122}, {\"ngram\": \"festivity\", \"from\": 7127, \"to\": 7136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing was related to religion at any point in time.\", \"from\": 7138, \"to\": 7191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nothing\", \"from\": 7138, \"to\": 7145}, {\"ngram\": \"religion\", \"from\": 7161, \"to\": 7169}, {\"ngram\": \"any point\", \"from\": 7173, \"to\": 7182}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 7186, \"to\": 7190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Done by \\\"South Park,\\\" \\\"The Simpsons,\\\" David LaChapelle.\", \"from\": 7193, \"to\": 7248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7202, \"end\": 7212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Park\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4897642216343256e-69, \"text\": \"South Park\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 7231, \"end\": 7247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_LaChapelle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David LaChapelle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_LaChapelle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_LaChapelle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because it was queer people and people of color all together.\", \"from\": 7250, \"to\": 7311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 7265, \"to\": 7277}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7282, \"to\": 7288}, {\"ngram\": \"color\", \"from\": 7292, \"to\": 7297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was about celebrating minorities.\", \"from\": 7312, \"to\": 7348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"minorities\", \"from\": 7337, \"to\": 7347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But what if it was \\\"The Last Supper\\\"?\", \"from\": 7349, \"to\": 7386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 7369, \"to\": 7384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Are queer people not allowed to also be believers and want that kind of representation?\", \"from\": 7387, \"to\": 7474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 7391, \"to\": 7403}, {\"ngram\": \"believers\", \"from\": 7427, \"to\": 7436}, {\"ngram\": \"that kind\", \"from\": 7446, \"to\": 7455}, {\"ngram\": \"representation\", \"from\": 7459, \"to\": 7473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not see why we should even feel bad about that, even though it was not the reference.\", \"from\": 7475, \"to\": 7565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reference\", \"from\": 7551, \"to\": 7564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I genuinely do not think that we have to apologize.\", \"from\": 7567, \"to\": 7618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I do understand that at the end of the day, the Olympics is supposed to bring peace and bring people together.\", \"from\": 7619, \"to\": 7733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 7647, \"to\": 7654}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 7658, \"to\": 7665}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 7667, \"to\": 7679}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 7701, \"to\": 7706}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7717, \"to\": 7723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And this was in the DNA of every action that we put into it.\", \"from\": 7734, \"to\": 7794, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the DNA\", \"from\": 7750, \"to\": 7757}, {\"ngram\": \"every action\", \"from\": 7761, \"to\": 7773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I understand that if they can ease up the tension that already exists so much around the world, they should.\", \"from\": 7795, \"to\": 7906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tension\", \"from\": 7836, \"to\": 7847}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 7883, \"to\": 7892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The activist that I am does not want to apologize, but I understand why the Olympics did.\", \"from\": 7907, \"to\": 7996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The activist\", \"from\": 7907, \"to\": 7919}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 7979, \"to\": 7991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To all the Christians that are allies to our community and never meant any harm to us, I apologize if you felt hurt or misinterpreted the art piece and our intentions.\", \"from\": 7998, \"to\": 8165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8009, \"end\": 8019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999062577747634, \"rank\": 9.370635910544942e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"allies\", \"from\": 8029, \"to\": 8035}, {\"ngram\": \"our community\", \"from\": 8039, \"to\": 8052}, {\"ngram\": \"any harm\", \"from\": 8069, \"to\": 8077}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8081, \"to\": 8083}, {\"ngram\": \"the art piece\", \"from\": 8132, \"to\": 8145}, {\"ngram\": \"our intentions\", \"from\": 8150, \"to\": 8164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope that now that there is more clarity you can enjoy the opening ceremony with no uncomfortable feelings.\", \"from\": 8166, \"to\": 8275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more clarity\", \"from\": 8196, \"to\": 8208}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 8223, \"to\": 8243}, {\"ngram\": \"no uncomfortable feelings\", \"from\": 8249, \"to\": 8274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To the ones that needed a blurry situation to unleash all their hatred and be openly transphobic, racist, fat-phobic and homophobic, we see you, we are used to you, and we are not scared of you.\", \"from\": 8277, \"to\": 8471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 8280, \"to\": 8288}, {\"ngram\": \"a blurry situation\", \"from\": 8301, \"to\": 8319}, {\"ngram\": \"all their hatred\", \"from\": 8331, \"to\": 8347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been called a groomer, a pedophile.\", \"from\": 8473, \"to\": 8515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a groomer\", \"from\": 8492, \"to\": 8501}, {\"ngram\": \"a pedophile\", \"from\": 8503, \"to\": 8514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been asked to look by the window because they will come for me, Like I said to one of these a--holes on social media who said \\\"Stay in France with your backward ideas,\\\" I said, \\\"I am actually a U.S. citizen as much as you are, and my voice in the next election counts as much as yours.\", \"from\": 8516, \"to\": 8808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8658, \"end\": 8664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999818859408948, \"rank\": 1.811305051104162e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 8717, \"end\": 8729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999920975399907, \"rank\": 7.902522616875279e-06, \"text\": \"U.S. citizen\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the window\", \"from\": 8545, \"to\": 8555}, {\"ngram\": \"these a--holes\", \"from\": 8609, \"to\": 8623}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 8627, \"to\": 8639}, {\"ngram\": \"your backward ideas\", \"from\": 8670, \"to\": 8689}, {\"ngram\": \"the next election counts\", \"from\": 8766, \"to\": 8790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See you at the voting booths!\\\"\", \"from\": 8809, \"to\": 8839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the voting booths\", \"from\": 8820, \"to\": 8837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Darling, I wash myself with their tears.\", \"from\": 8841, \"to\": 8881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their tears\", \"from\": 8869, \"to\": 8880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has never affected me whatsoever.\", \"from\": 8882, \"to\": 8918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because sadly queer people have had to be used to it.\", \"from\": 8919, \"to\": 8972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sadly queer people\", \"from\": 8927, \"to\": 8945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have always been targeted.\", \"from\": 8973, \"to\": 9002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, like I said, I like to take a shower in the morning with their tears.\", \"from\": 9003, \"to\": 9076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shower\", \"from\": 9035, \"to\": 9043}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 9047, \"to\": 9058}, {\"ngram\": \"their tears\", \"from\": 9064, \"to\": 9075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am fine with their tears.\", \"from\": 9077, \"to\": 9104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their tears\", \"from\": 9092, \"to\": 9103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was able to perform for 45 minutes on a bridge in the rain and we saw my mug did not move whatsoever.\", \"from\": 9105, \"to\": 9208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"45 minutes\", \"from\": 9131, \"to\": 9141}, {\"ngram\": \"a bridge\", \"from\": 9145, \"to\": 9153}, {\"ngram\": \"the rain\", \"from\": 9157, \"to\": 9165}, {\"ngram\": \"my mug\", \"from\": 9177, \"to\": 9183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am waterproof.\", \"from\": 9209, \"to\": 9225, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sean Hickey is an Associate Producer for TODAY with Hoda & Jenna.\", \"from\": 9227, \"to\": 9292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9227, \"end\": 9238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Hickey\", \"score\": 0.9999999975079845, \"rank\": 2.49155501604886e-09, \"text\": \"Sean Hickey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Hickey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sean_Hickey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Associate Producer\", \"from\": 9242, \"to\": 9263}, {\"ngram\": \"TODAY\", \"from\": 9268, \"to\": 9273}, {\"ngram\": \"Hoda\", \"from\": 9279, \"to\": 9283}, {\"ngram\": \"Jenna\", \"from\": 9286, \"to\": 9291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to producing broadcast segments with celebrities, social media stars, and stunts like Halloween costume reveals and original holiday songs, Sean also appears in front of the camera to host games.\", \"from\": 9293, \"to\": 9500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9445, \"end\": 9449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.o